msgid "The posterior odds have been corrected for multiple testing by fixing to 0.5 the prior probability that the null hypothesis holds across all comparisons (Westfall, Johnson, & Utts, 1997). Individual comparisons are based on the default t-test with a Cauchy (0, r = 1/sqrt(2)) prior. The \"U\" in the Bayes factor denotes that it is uncorrected."
msgstr ""
"Ganjil posterior telah dikoreksi untuk beberapa pengujian dengan memperbaiki "
"ke 0.5 probabilitas priori yang hipotesis null melintasi semua perbandingan "
"(Westfall, Johnson, & Utts, 1997). Perbandingan individu berdasarkan uji-t "
"bawaan dengan priori Cauchy (0, r = 1/sqrt(2)). \"U\" dalam faktor Bayes "
"menandakan bahwa itu tidak dikoreksikan."

